name: Dystopian Future
description:
Using the prompt "Environmental Impact Assessment", this artwork produced with artificial intelligence provides a  glimpse of a possible future reality through a dark fantasy lens, of what may become of our planet. 
Environmental Impact Assessment is a process of predicting and evaluating the impacts of proposed development on the environment. It is a tool used by governments to allow for development to go forward while minimizing and mitigating adverse environmental effects of the proposed projects. Unfortunately, the process often neglects to account for cumulative impacts which slowly contribute to the continued degradation of our planet. 
(Art generated with DREAM by Wombo AI)
